data.description: Looking for a place to call home that is affordable, peaceful and with space to spare? Check out this 1440 square foot, 3/2 manufactured home on three lots with a view that stretches for miles! City water/septic and solar panels provide affordable utility bill options and access to Lake LBJ and amenities are nearby. Tell your agent you'd like to own a piece of the Hill Country that won't break the bank.
